If I’m being honest, I judge a pipe maker by how well they can make a spoon. Too often do I see people overlook the small things that make a huge difference: 45* bowl push, carb at least twice the size of the bowl for proper airflow, etc... Perhaps I’m just being pretentious, but it really bums me out when I see an artist who makes incredible pieces turn out a derpy-looking spoon 💩Thanks for coming to my Ted Talk- piece sold to @chopdarkblues - #hatersgonnahate #spoonpipe #pipedreams #imjudgingyou
